The UI/UX of our digital platforms is a vital component of our mission to provide healing and wellness to our members. By optimizing the flow and aesthetic of our interfaces, we support our core values of truth, transparency, and member sovereignty. This document outlines the proposed enhancements for our landing page and member dashboard, aligning them with modern design principles and our healing mission.


