- **Member Dashboard:** Implement tooltips and dynamic user guides to enhance onboarding and engagement.


#### Modern Design Principles


- **Consistency:** Ensure uniformity in design elements across the platform to build user trust.
- **Accessibility:** Incorporate accessibility standards to make our platform usable for all members, reflecting our value of unity.
- **Performance:** Optimize assets and code to improve loading times, enhancing the user's experience.


