By enhancing the UI/UX of our platform, we align with the Forgotten Formula PMA's mission of true healing. These improvements will not only make our services more accessible and engaging but will also uphold our commitment to transparency, nature-first care, and member sovereignty. Our digital infrastructure should reflect the same care and precision we apply to our healing practices, ensuring every interaction supports our members' health and wellness journey.


